# Exclude large/sensitive directories
# [F17 2026-07-02] Root-anchored: the old unanchored `data/` also ignored the
# SOURCE package code/industreal_improved/src/data/ — which is why its
# __init__.py silently never made it into the repo and fresh clones could not
# run training. Dataset dirs at the repo root stay ignored.
/data/
external/

# Exclude logs and model files
*.log
*.pth
*.pt
*.pkl
*.h5

# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# Jupyter
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# OS
.DS_Store
*.swp
.gitnexus
